@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kqlhnp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v2))
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.28 - tmp + 0.77)) + wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.92)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.14)) / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
